{"tid":665694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Google 暫停為中興更新Android系統　禍及美數百萬手機用戶","createTime":"2018-05-15T07:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T09:09:46.000Z","uid":39464,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d635fcaf8688847d928ede19bb617519548f77ee","tid":665694,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T07:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180515/photo/bkncn-20180515153432247-0515_05011_001_01p.jpg?20180515153825\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180515%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180515153432247-0515_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180515153825&h=b3d1b7d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美貿易戰持續，美國此前封殺中國電訊廠中興通訊，實施7年的出口技術制裁，禁止美企向中興出售零件及軟件。據報，數百萬在美的中興手機用戶，已感受此制裁所影響，無法更新Google的安卓(Android)操作系統。 <br />\n<br />\n因應美國商務部實施的技術制裁，Google停止對中興通訊手機提供更新服務，導致用戶無法更新，及使用安卓系統提供的其他功能。據知情人士透露，有關服務中斷或致部分用戶無法操作手機。 <br />\n<br />\n根據數據顯示，去年初以來中興向美國市場出售近2500萬部智能手機，有部分手機用戶在社交媒體上抱怨，指「無法使用設備」，又稱他們或不得不放棄中興的手機，並轉用其他品牌。 <br />\n<br />\n此外，南非最大的電訊公司Vodacom Group Limited周一（14日）表示，當售罄現有存貨，後，不再銷售由中興生產的手機。Vodacom指，有關決定是中興通訊宣布暫停主要業務營運後作出的；而在相關問題獲解決前，Vodacom將停止銷售更多中興通訊的設備。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180515/bkncn-20180515153432247-0515_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180515%2Fbkncn-20180515153432247-0515_05011_001.html&d=oxW6gKhhKw4scgCLfX8DVMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=cc24e959\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180515/bkncn-20180515153432247-0515_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"dd1d34942fb1c500e84d8a97015ffb1d75a77722","tid":665694,"uid":41204,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T07:44:42.000Z","msg":"中共咁唔小心？唔係BAN GOOGLE既咩？<br />\nban剩android都得"},{"pid":"4279e4111bdeb2b31542a190a6ca7b04e37db9c9","tid":665694,"uid":47259,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T07:52:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根據數據顯示，去年初以來中興向美國市場出售近2500萬部智能手機，有部分手機用戶在社交媒體上抱怨，指「無法使用設備」，又稱他們或不得不放棄中興的手機，並轉用其他品牌。 </blockquote><br />\n正路就係要你咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係點知呢D有曬後門既電話幾時會變成支那發動網絡攻擊既僵屍device或者情報戰既竊聽器 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"057ca4562f9e93a81f1185685e1869aa3d2bca30","tid":665694,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T09:07:48.000Z","msg":"Trump<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85c43c6cdeecf811207917940dfb794fecd2e22","tid":665694,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T09:08:49.000Z","msg":"又話比左錢放生中興既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f767035e93b3bf2791c211ed4b13099162f9b9f","tid":665694,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T09:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75a95e2ef2b1f9a3a949ab99ebaf1a25bef77b4","tid":665694,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T09:09:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}